y 1994\nalign=centerJune 1994\nalign=centerRacing Club\nalign=center\nalign=centerMay 1995\nalign=centerNovember 1995\nalign=centerArgentina\nalign=center\nalign=centerNovember 2008\nalign=centerJuly 2010\nalign=centerAl-Wasl\nalign=center\nalign=centerMay 2011\nalign=centerJuly 2012\nalign=centerFujairah\nalign=center\nalign=centerApril 2017 \nalign=centerApril 2018 \nalign=centerDorados\nalign=center\nalign=centerSeptember 2018\nalign=centerJune 2019\nalign=centerGimnasia de La Plata\nalign=center\nalign=centerSeptember 2019\nalign=centerPresent\n!colspan=4Total\n\nBoca Juniors\nBULLET::::- Argentine Primera División: 1981 Metropolitano\n\nBarcelona\nBULLET::::- Copa del Rey: 1983\nBULLET::::- Copa de la Liga: 1983\n\nNapoli\nBULLET::::- Serie A (2): 1986–87, 1989–90\nBULLET::::- Coppa Italia: 1986–87\nBULLET::::- UEFA Cup: 1988–89\nBULLET::::- Supercoppa Italiana: 1990\n\nArgentina Youth\nBULLET::::- FIFA World Youth Championship: 1979\n\nArgentina\nBULLET::::- FIFA World Cup: 1986\nBULLET::::- Artemio Franchi Trophy: 1993\n\nBULLET::::- Argentine Primera División top scorers (5): 1978 Metropolitano, 1979 Metropolitano, 1979 Nacional, 1980 Metropolitano, 1980 Nacional\nBULLET::::- FIFA World Youth Championship Golden Ball: 1979\nBULLET::::- FIFA World Youth Championship Silver Shoe: 1979\nBULLET::::- Argentine Football Writers' Footballer of the Year (4): 1979, 1980, 1981, 1986\nBULLET::::- South American Footballer of the Year (2): (official award) 1979, 1980\nBULLET::::- Olimpia de Oro (2): 1979, 1986\nBULLET::::- Guerin d'Oro (Serie A Footballer of the Year): 1985\nBULLET::::- UNICEF European Footballer of the Season: 1989–90\nBULLET::::- FIFA World Cup Golden Ball: 1986\nBULLET::::- FIFA World Cup Silver Shoe: 1986\nBULLET::::- FIFA World Cup Most Assists: 1986\nBULLET::::- FIFA World Cup All-Star Team (2): 1986, 1990\nBULLET::::- Onze d'Or (2): 1986, 1987\nBULLET::::- L'Équipe Champion of Champions: 1986\nBULLET::::- United Press International Athlete of the